OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780945878
OL,3,CDisclosure Day: Steven Spielberg
OL,4,Creturns with new alien blockbuster
OL,6,FITV News Entertainment Reporter Rishi
OL,7,FDavda sits down with Steven Spielberg
OL,8,Fand Josh O'Connor ahead of the UK
OL,9,Flaunch of sci-fi thriller Disclosure
OL,10,FDay
OL,12,FSteven Spielberg knows how to make a
OL,13,Fmovie. He's got the Oscars, BAFTAs and
OL,14,FGolden Globes to prove it. The
OL,15,Ffilmmaker's trophy case also boasts
OL,16,FEmmys, a Tony and a Grammy.
OL,18,FThe 79-year-old is part of the elite
OL,19,FEGOT (Emmy, Grammy, Oscar, Tony)
OL,20,Fwinners community. I do sometimes
OL,21,Fwonder if they have a group chat?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
