OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780945878
OL,3,CDisclosure Day: Steven Spielberg
OL,4,Creturns with new alien blockbuster
OL,6,FHe's masterminded so many iconic
OL,7,Ffilms, including Jurassic Park, E.T.,
OL,8,Fthe Indiana Jones franchise, Jaws,
OL,9,FSaving Private Ryan and my own
OL,10,Fpersonal favourite The Terminal. The
OL,11,Ffull list is way way longer.
OL,13,FSpielberg's newest film is Disclosure
OL,14,FDay, which details the race to reveal
OL,15,Fthe truth about the existence of
OL,16,Faliens.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
