PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780945878
OL,3,CDisclosure Day: Steven Spielberg
OL,4,Creturns with new alien blockbuster
OL,6,FThe director was inspired to make the
OL,7,Ffilm almost a decade ago, when media
OL,8,Foutlets in the US started to report on
OL,9,Fthe Pentagon's secretive attempts to
OL,10,Fsecure testimony from pilots and other
OL,11,FUS military personnel who claimed to
OL,12,Fhave seen peculiar objects flying in
OL,13,Fthe sky.
OL,15,FSpielberg told me that "when the
OL,16,Fmainstream media started taking this
OL,17,Fseriously, it rekindled in 2017, my
OL,18,Finterest, which was reflected in
OL,19,F'Close Encounters of the Third Kind',
OL,20,Fand then 'E.T.' and 'War of the
OL,21,FWorlds'."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
