OL,3,CDisclosure Day: Steven Spielberg
OL,4,Creturns with new alien blockbuster
OL,6,FWhen asked if working alongside
OL,7,FSpielberg on Disclosure Day had
OL,8,Fchanged his perception of the
OL,9,Fpotential of extraterrestrial life,
OL,10,FO'Connor says he was "always open to"
OL,11,Fthe idea of other lifeforms.
OL,13,F"If you look up at the sky at night,
OL,14,Fit's very east to imagine that we're
OL,15,Fprobably not alone....the information
OL,16,Fis out there. I'm just kind of curious
OL,17,Fto have more of it released."
OL,26,@rD@VOUrD@eO]uD@AOUyD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
