PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780945878
OL,3,CDisclosure Day: Steven Spielberg
OL,4,Creturns with new alien blockbuster
OL,6,FShould the time eventually come that
OL,7,Fthe existence of aliens is officially
OL,8,Fconfirmed, Spielberg believes there
OL,9,Fwould be a "variety of responses".
OL,11,F"Some people will say 'I knew all
OL,12,Falong and I've been preparing myself
OL,13,Fall along, and it doesn't disturb me'.
OL,15,F"Other people will feel an ontological
OL,16,Fshock of social dislocation, that this
OL,17,Fis turning what I consider to be a
OL,18,Ffundamental reality upside down and
OL,19,Fwould not handle it well. Everybody
OL,20,Fwould have a unique reaction."
OL,26,@qD@LOUqD@aO]sD@AOUwD@AOU|D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
