OL,3,CDisclosure Day: Steven Spielberg
OL,4,Creturns with new alien blockbuster
OL,6,FO'Connor was drawn to Disclosure Day
OL,7,Ffor two reasons, firstly there's the
OL,8,FSpielberg element.
OL,10,F"I don't think you can take out the
OL,11,FStephen factor. A director who has a
OL,12,Fclear vision is always very attractive
OL,13,Fand helpful."
OL,15,FThe 36-year-old is also keen that his
OL,16,Ffilmography mirrors that of his idols.
OL,26,@rD@AOUuD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
