PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780945878
OL,3,CDisclosure Day: Steven Spielberg
OL,4,Creturns with new alien blockbuster
OL,6,F"I think the actors that I aspire to,
OL,7,Fpeople like Tom Hanks, Robin Williams,
OL,8,FGene Wilder, people who have had
OL,9,Fdiverse careers where they can do
OL,10,Fcomedy and then they can do tragedy,
OL,11,Fthey can do action."
OL,13,F"I think about the young version of me
OL,14,Fat drama school and why I was so drawn
OL,15,Fto Shakespeare. You have that
OL,16,Fdiversity of character across
OL,17,FShakespeare's works or in the theatre."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@TO]uD@AOUyD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
