PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780945878
OL,3,CDisclosure Day: Steven Spielberg
OL,4,Creturns with new alien blockbuster
OL,6,FTheatre is very much a traditional art
OL,7,Fform that has stood the test of time.
OL,8,FAs movies evolve and embrace new
OL,9,Ftechnology, Spielberg is still on the
OL,10,Fside of traditional tricks.
OL,12,FIn Disclosure Day, Emily Blunt briefly
OL,13,Fdelivers dialogue in an entirely made
OL,14,Fup alien language.
OL,16,F"I would never have made that choice,"
OL,17,FSteven reveals. "Even if Emily was
OL,18,Funable to produce the sounds that she
OL,19,Fdid produce organically, I would never
OL,20,Fhave used AI (artificial
OL,21,Fintelligence)."
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@fO]yD@QOU}D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
