SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780945878
OL,3,CDisclosure Day: Steven Spielberg
OL,4,Creturns with new alien blockbuster
OL,6,F"I would have probably gone the old-
OL,7,Ffashioned way. You get a dolphin or
OL,8,Fyou get an elephant and you slow it
OL,9,Fdown, or you speed it up or you play
OL,10,Fit backwards."
OL,12,FSpielberg has been churning out flicks
OL,13,Fsince the 60s, pretty much all of
OL,14,Fwhich would have been accompanied by a
OL,15,Ftrailer.
OL,17,FThere's a skill to the perfect 2-
OL,18,Fminute teaser, that in recent years
OL,19,Fseems to have been watered down to
OL,20,Fbasically give away the whole plot.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
