PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780945878
OL,3,CDisclosure Day: Steven Spielberg
OL,4,Creturns with new alien blockbuster
OL,6,F"I don't believe in that", he laughs.
OL,7,F"The sign for me of a good trailer
OL,8,Fbasically is less is more. It's just
OL,9,Fkind of priming the engine of public
OL,10,Finterest."
OL,12,F"Some audiences like to see the whole
OL,13,Ffilm in two and a half minutes...but
OL,14,Fthe element of surprise is missing.
OL,15,FThe element of surprise is the whole
OL,16,Freason I got into movies to begin
OL,17,Fwith."
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@YO]oD@AOUrD@JO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
