OL,3,CDisclosure Day: Steven Spielberg
OL,4,Creturns with new alien blockbuster
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FHe's still a purist when it comes to
OL,12,Fthe movie business, which he holds so
OL,13,Fdear. While streamers favour small
OL,14,Fscreens, Spielberg likes them large.
OL,16,F"The idea of sending little cassettes,
OL,17,Flittle DVDs to individuals to watch a
OL,18,Fmovie, if I did that, I would be happy
OL,19,Fto work for Netflix and make a movie
OL,20,Ffor Netflix."
OL,26,@xD@AOU|D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
