OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780945878
OL,3,CDisclosure Day: Steven Spielberg
OL,4,Creturns with new alien blockbuster
OL,6,F"I'd know it's only going to be seen
OL,7,Fby millions of people on their home
OL,8,Fscreens. But, I'm a movie maker and I
OL,9,Fbelieve in big motion pictures, 70
OL,10,Fmillimetre theatrical releases."
OL,12,FDisclosure Day is in cinemas from
OL,13,FWednesday June 10.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@`O]
